         log(F_p) = 4.4886, log-approx (formal) = 52071.7500
  p=13: F_p = 233.0000, Σe_r = 233.0000, S₂ = 21.0000, e₁ = 21.0000
         log(F_p) = 5.4510, log-approx (formal) = -4044394.7167

